data.description:
Amazing single story home. Spacious great room. Beautiful kitchen is open to the great room. Kitchen offers plenty of cabinetry with granite counter tops, upgrades include backsplash, pendant lights and extended pantry. Side by side ss refrigerator, gas range, microwave & dishwasher. Zoned master suite includes a spacious walk in closet, double sink vanity, three shower heads were added glass door to the ceiling, shower and bench.
Beautiful upgraded -complete backyard landscape design with fire pit  added irrigation and drip system, additional electrical outlets, and gazebo. Double car garage w/auto door opener.
